Responsibilities

ByteDance will be prioritizing applicants who have a current right to work in Singapore, and do not require ByteDance's sponsorship of a visa.

About Us

Founded in 2012, ByteDance's mission is to inspire creativity and enrich life. With a suite of more than a dozen products, including TikTok, Helo, and Resso, as well as platforms specific to the China market, including Toutiao, Douyin, and Xigua, ByteDance has made it easier and more fun for people to connect with, consume, and create content.

Why Join Us

At ByteDance, our people are humble, intelligent, compassionate and creative. We create to inspire - for you, for us, and for millions of users across all of our products. We lead with curiosity and aim for the highest, never shying away from taking calculated risks and embracing ambiguity as it comes. Here, the opportunities are limitless for those who dare to pursue bold ideas that exist just beyond the boundary of possibility. Join us and make impact happen with a career at ByteDance.

About The Team

Corporate System is based on the needs of the company's internal system construction and responsible for the planning and construction of internal human resources, finance, legal affairs, procurement, approval and other internal systems, demand and project management, information security management, system configuration, operation and maintenance of the company.

 Complete the request management and implementation systems based on business needs, such as HCM, legal , contract, OA and other systems;
 Responsible for the functional implementation of the aPaaS system (low-code platform), low-code and interface development;
 In-depth exploration and analysis of business needs, write technical solutions and system designs, implement the design solutions as specific platform functions, continuously track results, and continuously optimize User Experience;
 Responsible for low-code business model building, forming a common method and application framework to reuse;
 Internal implementation of capacity training, knowledge transfer.

Qualifications

 Be able to independently complete demand analysis, business design and other work, lead or participate in demand review work, and answer questions raised in demand review;
 Be able to convert business requirements into software system requirements, analyze the feasibility and rationality of business requirements, communicate with developers in a timely manner, and issue product demand analysis results based on accurate logical analysis;
 Interested in or have relevant experience in zero-code and low-code directions; familiar with a language such as Node.js / / Python /Go/ Java , good coding taste, able to produce high-quality design and code;
 Positive and optimistic, strong sense of responsibility, careful and meticulous work, good team communication and collaboration skills.

ByteDance is committed to creating an inclusive space where employees are valued for their skills, experiences, and unique perspectives. Our platform connects people from across the globe and so does our workplace. At ByteDance, our mission is to inspire creativity and enrich life. To achieve that goal, we are committed to celebrating our diverse voices and to creating an environment that reflects the many communities we reach. We are passionate about this and hope you are too.

Job Responsibilities:

Develop features for mobile games based on the Unity3D engine;
Assist in developing game-related extension kits, engine application components, and engine component library construction;
Responsible for the development of game client-related logic.


Requirements:

Diploma or above in a computer-related major; game demo production experience required;
Proficient in U3D engine architecture design and object-oriented programming in C#, Lua, C++, and Java, with strong logical thinking ability;
Familiarity with basic algorithms, such as physics algorithms, and knowledge about computer graphics, Unity graphic processing processes, and Unity rendering optimization-related work;
Passionate about games, loves life, and eager to make successful games.

