The System Technologies and Engineering team is looking for experienced AIOps driven DevOps Engineer in the area of system software management in the large scale Data Center. This individual will work with our global team to develop, deploy, and conduct maintenance of the infrastructure management platform, which mainly focuses in the areas of system software, such as server firmware, operation systems, Operating System (OS), kernel, performance profiling, diagnosis and troubleshooting systems.

