 Develop and optimise algorithms and softwares for fault and anomaly detection, self-healing systems, monitoring and alarm systems, etc.;
 Regularly collaborate with engineers to gather and implement requirements and participate in functional architecture design discussions;
 Optimise the operational efficiency, cost and quality by exploring various means from the automation engineering and AIOps perspective;
 Advocate continuous improvement and operational excellence practices within the team;
 Conduct emergency response for faults or failures related to the platform and the system software;

