 Bachelor's degree or above, major in Computer Science or related;
 At least 3+ years of experiences in large scale operation and management system platform development experience or in similar fields;
 Working knowledge of Data Center Infrastructure including but not limited to servers, networking, switches etc;
 Familiar with one or more general purpose programming languages such as Go, Python, Java, Golang is preferred but not necessary;
 Working knowledge with common components such as Nginx, Clickhouse, Victoria Metrics, MySQL, Kafka, Flink, etc;
 Possesses a strong foundation in coding style, system design document writing and task management;

