About Tencent
Tencent is an Internet-based platform company founded in Shenzhen, China, in 1998. We use technology to enrich the lives of Internet users and assist the digital upgrade of enterprises. Our mission is "Value for Users, Tech for Good". We embrace a culture of teamwork & creativity and are driven by our values - Integrity, Proactivity, Collaboration and Creativity.
We are rapidly expanding our international operations and are looking for top talent to propel us forward. Combining the results-oriented nature of a startup with the resources of a profitable and leading Internet company, Tencent offers a unique opportunity for aspiring individuals to thrive.

Department introduction:
Since the first Hadoop cluster was built in January 2009, Tencent Data Platform Department has continuously explored and practiced with the mission of "data-driven, maximizing business value". At present, the platform's computing power elastic resource pool has exceeded 200,000 units, and every day The number of data access pieces reaches 35 trillion pieces, forming a set of data service-oriented platforms around the full life cycle of data; at the same time, it provides mass, real-time, and accurate personalized recommendation services driven by full-process data for the company's advertising business, providing Tencent Each business outputs professional data foundation and application solutions.

Responsibilities:
Responsible for the operation and maintenance of big data cluster (Hadoop Hbase Hive Yarn Spark, etc.);
Responsible for cluster performance optimization, expansion and contraction;
Responsible for cluster monitoring and alarm, fault handling, data backup, user problem handling, etc.;

Requirements:
Bachelor's degree in Computer Science or a related field
Ideally with experience in big data cluster operation and maintenance;
Proficient in any language in Python Shell Java, familiar with Linux development environment and corresponding configuration, management and optimization;
Familiar with TCP/IP, HTTP and other protocols, and have good knowledge of network, security, database, computer architecture.
Fluent in Chinese and English is preferred in order to communicate with various stakeholders in headquarters

