Speech & Audio (SA) team provides industry-leading ML algorithm capabilities and complete voice product solutions for all business lines, including B2B as well. We empower businesses in the fields of speech/song synthesis, audio understanding, music intelligence, etc., and solve basic problems such as audio and video content understanding and creation, music information retrieval, and human-computer voice interaction.

The Backend Engineer team of music intelligence group is committed to promoting the cutting-edge backend system of music information retrieval (MIR) and music content understanding, following up the leading engineering work in the industry, improving the engineering influence and building technical barriers of SA team in related fields.

Responsibilities:
- Design and build a cutting-edge music retrieval system architecture to support the development and performance optimisation of music retrieval systems with large-scale music databases;
- Create a high-performance music system algorithm engine, which will be based on a high-performance deep learning inference framework;
- Build an ultra-large-scale online service cluster to support ultra-high concurrent online music service traffic;
- Support the landing of cutting-edge algorithms and apply them to actual business;
- Deploy and maintain services with physical machine clusters; 

